---
title: Beef & Mushroom Ragu Cannelloni with Pear-Rocket Salad & Garlicky Greens
description: This dish is wrapped and stacked with juicy flavours that we can’t get enough of. Gooey Parmesan cheese is melted
over cannelloni that’s been stuffed with a tomato-based beef filling with pops of veggies in every bite to make your
mouth water. Enough waiting, let’s eat!

